        <abstract> 
<p>Sends MS of his chapter on geology for <hi rend="italic">Manual</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 227–50]. Fears it may be too long. Does not much like it but can do no better. After hesitation, has recommended books. Defends his point that mere collection of rock specimens is "of hardly any use to Geology".</p> 
        </abstract>
